# Tracking — provide these once Tahir sends the IDs.
# Each script only loads when its var is set; leave blank to skip.
# GTM_ID               → Google Tag Manager container  (e.g. GTM-XXXXXXX)
# GA4_ID               → Google Analytics 4            (e.g. G-XXXXXXXXXX)
# CLARITY_ID           → Microsoft Clarity             (e.g. xxxxxxxxxx)
# GOOGLE_ADS_ID        → Google Ads account tag        (e.g. AW-XXXXXXXXX)
# GADS_CONV_LABEL      → Conversion action label       (e.g. AbCdEfGhIjK)
#                        In Google Ads → Goals → Conversion actions → Tag details
